    fix: clip calorie/burn rings in CaloriesTab — R exceeded viewBox for stroke
    
    R=54 placed the circle path at 1px from each edge of the 110x110
    viewBox. The 9px stroke is centered on the path, so the outer half of
    the stroke extended to -3.5px outside the viewBox on every side —
    clipped by the SVG canvas. Both the calorie and burn rings lost their
    outer curve on all four sides.
    
    Reduce R to 48 so the outer stroke edge sits 2.5px inside the viewBox,
    matching the working pattern at line 1581 (R=44, viewBox=100, stroke=8
    → 2px clearance).
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>

